    dc:title "Taxonomy and distribution of a common arboreal lizard, Bronchocela jubata Duméril & Bibron, 1837 (Reptilia: Agamidae), with designation of its lectotype from Java, Indonesia" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6609935>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6609937>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6609941>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6609927> ;
