<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6609935>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Bronchocela jubata lectotype (MNHN-RA 2542, adult male) from Java: (A) lateral view of the full body, (B) dorsal head, (C) lateral head, (D) ventral head." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6609935/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6609937>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Bronchocela jubata (A) in life (adult male, not collected) from Cibinong near Bogor, West Java." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6609937/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6609941>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Sulcate view of the left hemipenis of Bronchocela jubata (MZB 6639) from Sukamantri, Bogor, West Java." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6609941/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6609927>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Current distribution map showing the collection/observation localities of Bronchocela jubata (red) and its sympatric congener, B. cristatella sensu lato (blue) on Java and Bali Islands; sympatric localities filled partially; for the distribution of B. jubata on Sumatra Island, see Amarasinghe et al. 2022." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6609927/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

